ID: How to diffentiate task from task, recommend using numbers respectively. Eg: 1; 2; 3; 4
Title: What type is the task. Eg: Study; Household chores; Club
Detail: What is the task about. Eg: Doing calculus II homework, exercise 2.1-2.10
Priority: How important is the task. Scale: 1-5, 1 - most important, 5 - least important. Eg: 3
Deadline: When will it be finished, only mm/dd/yyyy. Eg: 31/02/2025
